============================================================
PHASE 3 OBJECTIVE
============================================================

Build a complete risk protection system for zDash.

Main goals:

1. Create Guardian Agent
2. Add drawdown calculation
3. Add account equity/balance tracking model
4. Add emergency stop threshold
5. Add halt flag system
6. Add manual halt and resume controls
7. Integrate Guardian risk approval into trading execution engine
8. Add risk audit logs
9. Add FastAPI risk endpoints
10. Add tests for all risk-critical behavior

IMPORTANT:
- This system must default to safe mode.
- Live trading must remain disabled by default.
- DRY_RUN must remain true by default.
- No execution is allowed when risk halt is active.
- No execution is allowed if Guardian approval fails.
- Do not provide financial advice.
- This is a technical risk-control implementation for simulation, paper trading, and guarded automation.

