============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update `.env.example` with:

RISK_GUARDIAN_ENABLED=true

MAX_DAILY_DRAWDOWN_PERCENT=5
MAX_TOTAL_DRAWDOWN_PERCENT=20
EMERGENCY_KILL_SWITCH_DRAWDOWN_PERCENT=50

SOFT_HALT_DRAWDOWN_LEVEL_1=5
SOFT_HALT_DRAWDOWN_LEVEL_2=10
SOFT_HALT_DRAWDOWN_LEVEL_3=20

ALLOW_MANUAL_RESUME=true
REQUIRE_RESUME_REASON=true

DRY_RUN=true
LIVE_TRADING_ACK=false

Rules:

- Values must be parsed from environment variables.
- Invalid config values must fail safely.
- If config is missing, use safe defaults.
- Emergency stop threshold must be configurable but default to 50%.
- Soft halt thresholds must default to 5%, 10%, and 20%.

